      "text": "⚠️ Criticisms and Concerns",
      "id": 10,
      "description": "<p data-start=\"1650\" data-end=\"1735\" class=\"\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Economists have raised several concerns about this approach:</span>​<span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/world/trumps-tariff-formula-confounds-world-punishes-poor-2025-04-03/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"flex h-6 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2.5 text-[0.5625em] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">WSJ</span><span class=\"ms-1 -me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+3</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\"><br></span></span></span></a></span></p>\n<ol data-start=\"1737\" data-end=\"2225\">\n<li data-start=\"1737\" data-end=\"1849\" class=\"\">\n<p data-start=\"1740\" data-end=\"1849\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"1740\" data-end=\"1762\">Oversimplification</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The formula reduces complex trade relationships to a single metric, ignoring factors like services trade, investment flows, and non-tariff barriers.</span>​<span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><br></span></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1851\" data-end=\"1980\" class=\"\">\n<p data-start=\"1854\" data-end=\"1980\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"1854\" data-end=\"1893\">Misinterpretation of Trade Deficits</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Trade deficits are not inherently negative and can result from various factors, including consumer preferences and economic structures.</span>​<br></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1982\" data-end=\"2101\" class=\"\">\n<p data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2101\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"1985\" data-end=\"2014\">Potential for Retaliation</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Imposing tariffs based on this formula could provoke retaliatory measures from trading partners, leading to trade wars.</span>​<br></p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"2103\" data-end=\"2225\" class=\"\">\n<p data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2225\" class=\"\"><strong data-start=\"2106\" data-end=\"2138\">Impact on Developing Nations</strong>: <span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">The formula disproportionately affects poorer countries with limited capacity to import U.S. goods, potentially harming their economies.</span>​<br></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p data-start=\"2227\" data-end=\"2312\" class=\"\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">For instance, countries like Lesotho and Cambodia faced tariffs of nearly 50%, despite their minimal impact on the U.S. trade balance.</span></p>",
